{
    "id": "welcome/howtodoquests",
    "title": "How to do quests",
    "description": "Learn how quest mechanics work, including dialogue choices, real items, and safe processes.",
    "image": "/assets/quests/how_to_do_quests_flowchart.jpg",
    "npc": "/assets/npc/dChat.jpg",
    "start": "start",
    "dialogue": [
        {
            "id": "start",
            "text": "Whirr-click! dChat online. I'm your pint-sized hype unit and quest coach. Ready for Quest Tutorial v1.0? Bonus confetti included.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "garage",
                    "text": "Wait, why are you in my garage?"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "yourquest",
                    "text": "A quest, you say? Tell me more."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "garage",
            "text": "A heroic delivery drone dropped me off after your order. I live in your garage now. It's cozy and full of sockets.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "delivery",
                    "text": "Ah, it's all coming back to me now..."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "delivery",
            "text": "No worries! I sip power, I don't guzzle it. I'll stay local-only, no cloud snooping. Keep me dry, keep me cool, and we are best friends forever.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "dialogueoptions",
                    "text": "Great! So, what's the deal with this quest you mentioned?"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "yourquest",
            "text": "Your quest? Master the ancient art of questing. It's easy, but I adore a good tutorial sequence.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "expert",
                    "text": "I got this, no need for a tutorial!"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "dialogueoptions",
                    "text": "Alright, lay it on me, dChat."
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "expert",
            "text": "Aha! A seasoned adventurer. Say the word and we speedrun. But still: unplug devices before adding a smart plug. Safety is the real loot.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "grantsItems",
                    "grantsItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "a5395e29-1862-4eb7-8517-5d161635e032",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ],
                    "text": "What's this?"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "a5395e29-1862-4eb7-8517-5d161635e032",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ],
                    "goto": "shortcircuit",
                    "text": "Alright, now can I skip?"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "shortcircuit",
            "text": "Okay! Skipping to the credits... wait, no credits. I'll just awkwardly wave.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "finish",
                    "text": "Bye, dChat!"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "dialogueoptions",
            "text": "Step one: choices. Pick an option, branch the story, unlock rewards. You're basically the director.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "items",
                    "text": "What's next?"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "items",
            "text": "Some choices hand you items instantly. Others unlock only when you have the goods. Here—digital tokens. Zero carbon, 100% sparkle.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "grantsItems",
                    "grantsItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "d88ef09c-9191-4c18-8628-a888bb9f926d",
                            "count": 10
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "5247a603-294a-4a34-a884-1ae20969b2a1",
                            "count": 100
                        }
                    ],
                    "text": "Great, free stuff! Thanks!"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "processes",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "d88ef09c-9191-4c18-8628-a888bb9f926d",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ],
                    "text": "Like this, right?"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "processes",
            "text": "Boom! You're a quick learner. Next: processes. They can need items, make items, and take time. Start the smart plug process I gave you and hand over the final product. Make sure the wall outlet is dry and not overloaded before you plug in the smart plug.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "grantsItems",
                    "grantsItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "a5395e29-1862-4eb7-8517-5d161635e032",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ],
                    "text": "Looks like I need this to finish the process."
                },
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "outlet-dWatt-1e3",
                    "text": "Start the smart plug process to buy 1 kWh"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "hangofthis",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "061fd221-404a-4bd1-9432-3e25b0f17a2c",
                            "count": 3000
                        }
                    ],
                    "text": "dWatt...? What's this?"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "hangofthis",
            "text": "You're really getting the hang of this. I'm impressed! If you need a refresher, just yell 'Quest-a-rific!' I'll be here in your garage. Have some cold, hard digital cash. Any questions before we wrap? Remember to disconnect the smart plug when you're done.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "finish",
                    "text": "Nope, I'm good. Thanks for the help!"
                }
            ]
        }
    ],
